OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudier this evening with showers
OL,7,Fpushing into the west. Then gradually
OL,8,Fbecoming wet and windy through the
OL,9,Fearly hours with widespread outbreaks
OL,10,Fof rain. A mild night to come.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAn unsettled start with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,14,Fpersistent over the moors. Somewhat
OL,15,Fdrier and brighter into the afternoon
OL,16,Fthrough still drizzle in places. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
